I miss the old videos... when the thumbnails weren’t always the same thing (Lew in the background and blurred out) and when the videos started when he was sitting down in the set. The way that the videos start out now (handheld) seems less professional than you guys are. I would love it if you guys did one stationary angle, and an other handheld angle for the videos. I doubt y’all would listen to me, but please do. I hope other fans think the same thing that I do.
Edit: if others watching this video want to respond in an angry manner, please don’t. I’m not trying to be mean to the people at Unbox Therapy, I’m just respectfully giving them constructive criticism. Thanks 👍
